WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 10=

01:39.056 --> 01:40.240
Travels Across the Four Seas?

01:41.136 --> 01:42.936
I read this book when I was a child.

01:44.335 --> 01:48.936
The fifth volume is about the adventures
in the Dragon Bone Desert.

01:49.735 --> 01:52.095
Back then, when Master Wuchen
crossed a sandbank here,

01:52.416 --> 01:53.856
he met a Western Divine Maiden

01:53.856 --> 01:56.735
wearing a skull necklace
at the sixth bend, Dragon Claw Bay.

01:57.136 --> 02:00.296
The red-eyed sand fox she raised
could smell the scent of the dead.

02:00.296 --> 02:00.815
It also...

02:00.815 --> 02:01.535
Sleep.

02:10.536 --> 02:11.816
But I can't sleep.

02:19.256 --> 02:20.335
Did you hear that?

02:21.895 --> 02:23.416
The sound of a night owl.

02:26.856 --> 02:27.655
Your Highness,

02:28.895 --> 02:30.256
are you afraid of night owls?

02:32.455 --> 02:33.895
I was very afraid as a child.

02:35.136 --> 02:36.848
I always felt their calls

02:37.626 --> 02:39.016
sounded like wails from demons.

02:42.296 --> 02:43.895
But as I grew, I stopped being afraid.

02:45.096 --> 02:48.016
I even found their calls quite amusing.

02:56.615 --> 02:57.536
Won't you keep reading?

02:58.335 --> 02:59.735
I'd like to chat a bit more.

03:00.136 --> 03:01.296
We can chat lying down.

03:18.256 --> 03:19.215
Your hand is so cold.

03:19.536 --> 03:20.416
Are you very cold?

03:22.536 --> 03:24.655
The mountain night chill
is most treacherous.

03:25.536 --> 03:27.735
It seeps through every seam of clothing.

03:29.536 --> 03:33.096
When I was on Lishan Mountain, I often
couldn't sleep because of the cold.

03:34.256 --> 03:36.055
Qingshuang always held me to sleep.

03:38.335 --> 03:39.416
Your maid?

03:40.136 --> 03:40.935
Yes.

03:41.935 --> 03:43.816
Qingshuang loved the fire before sleep.

03:44.536 --> 03:46.016
She was always warm.

03:46.016 --> 03:48.720
♪Amidst life's ups and downs,
turns and twists♪

03:48.720 --> 03:52.777
♪Love has never strayed away♪

03:53.552 --> 03:55.136
♪Throughout this lifetime♪

03:55.136 --> 03:56.735
Your Highness is also warm.

04:00.304 --> 04:03.248
♪Countless trials and pleadings,
right or wrong♪

04:03.248 --> 04:07.683
♪Try to make this love quiet♪

04:08.592 --> 04:10.416
♪But we fight back♪

04:10.416 --> 04:17.232
♪To make it a tale to be told♪

04:17.520 --> 04:21.520
♪Deepest love is none other than♪

04:21.520 --> 04:23.376
♪Aligning my scars with yours♪

04:23.376 --> 04:24.987
♪What was once let go♪

04:24.987 --> 04:27.009
♪Will heal together from now on♪

04:27.009 --> 04:28.666
♪From your silhouette♪

04:28.666 --> 04:32.257
♪I see the same me♪

04:32.257 --> 04:35.600
♪If dreams become illusions♪

04:35.600 --> 04:38.256
♪With you I journey and find solace♪

04:38.256 --> 04:39.835
♪In the sole abode of heart♪

04:39.835 --> 04:41.824
♪We embrace and circle into a corner♪

04:41.824 --> 04:43.661
♪Among worldly entanglements♪

04:43.661 --> 04:48.023
♪Love lightly brushes past♪

04:48.944 --> 04:50.956
♪None better than you,
and none better than me♪

04:51.310 --> 04:59.243
♪Love blooms at every spring and sunset♪

05:03.792 --> 05:09.712
(Awakening to Truth)

06:02.616 --> 06:04.016
This is your mother's grave?

06:04.975 --> 06:05.775
Yes.

06:07.215 --> 06:09.360
I thought she had long returned
to Lishan Mountain.

06:10.655 --> 06:12.975
Back then, Father and Mother separated.

06:13.736 --> 06:16.696
Mother was consumed
by anger and fell ill.

06:17.335 --> 06:18.496
She was cast out.

06:19.616 --> 06:23.256
Fortunately, the Abbot helped us
and let her stay here for treatment.

06:26.095 --> 06:26.895
Unfortunately,

06:27.736 --> 06:29.576
Mother still couldn't make it through.

06:30.975 --> 06:32.256
She passed away.

06:34.816 --> 06:36.016
Can you help me up?

06:46.016 --> 06:49.056
Mother-in-law, I, your son-in-law
Mo Xiuyao, pay my respects.

06:59.415 --> 07:00.215
Mom,

07:03.016 --> 07:04.936
I still wear
the Double-Fish Jade Pendant

07:06.095 --> 07:07.136
you gave me.

07:08.016 --> 07:11.655
You said you hoped one day
I would find a good husband.

07:12.136 --> 07:13.455
I've found one.

07:16.256 --> 07:17.655
This is my husband.

07:19.215 --> 07:20.455
He treats me very well.

07:20.855 --> 07:22.256
We share the same interests.

07:23.256 --> 07:25.215
And my sister-in-law is very gentle

07:25.655 --> 07:26.736
and treats me kindly.

07:28.056 --> 07:30.736
And I have a little nephew.

07:31.215 --> 07:33.855
He has quite a temper
but is clever and adorable.

07:36.655 --> 07:37.855
I am very content

07:38.816 --> 07:39.936
with my life.

07:42.256 --> 07:43.775
I hope, knowing from the heavens,

07:45.616 --> 07:46.855
you can rest assured now.

07:52.496 --> 07:56.656
(Tomb of Xu Wanzhou, Beloved Mother)

07:58.215 --> 07:59.455
Your mother passed away here.

07:59.816 --> 08:01.335
How did you return to Lishan Mountain?

08:03.215 --> 08:04.736
Qingshuang accompanied me back.

08:06.016 --> 08:08.056
We were thoroughly searched at its foot.

08:08.455 --> 08:10.616
All the valuables with us were seized.

08:11.256 --> 08:13.455
Even the hairpins were taken.

08:14.215 --> 08:16.016
Only two Double-Fish Jade Pendants
remained.

08:17.376 --> 08:20.256
Then the soldiers let us go up.

08:24.455 --> 08:26.136
Your Highness, are you pitying me?

08:26.975 --> 08:28.215
You don't need to pity me.

08:28.775 --> 08:31.775
Meeting Your Highness
is my greatest fortune.

08:48.216 --> 08:55.736
♪Formless realms and mist gather here♪

08:56.456 --> 09:02.175
♪Beneath the green lotus brush
lies past cause♪

09:04.775 --> 09:12.336
♪Seven layers of clouds
refract the lamplight♪

09:13.016 --> 09:18.695
♪The ninefold scented air
distinguishes worldly dust♪

09:21.336 --> 09:29.136
♪Sleeves hide a world formed in void♪

09:29.575 --> 09:34.775
♪Brows hold the sun and moon
beyond time♪

09:37.695 --> 09:40.775
Senior Wei Zhuang,
what are they doing here?

09:41.616 --> 09:45.055
We have gathered here because of
the 'Divine Maiden Downcast Gaze' mural.

09:45.616 --> 09:47.136
That's how this mural was finished.

09:47.376 --> 09:49.935
Now that it's done,
we are about to part ways.

09:50.376 --> 09:51.655
We held this Shang Yu Feast.

09:52.616 --> 09:53.856
Drunk, we sing and lament.

09:54.616 --> 09:55.815
Sober, we say our farewells.

09:56.616 --> 10:04.736
♪Tomorrow, we tread separate paths
through the vast sand♪

10:05.295 --> 10:13.256
♪One scroll of profound wisdom
speaks eternal spring♪

10:14.216 --> 10:15.016
Bravo!

10:15.016 --> 10:17.336
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

10:18.016 --> 10:19.216
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

10:28.216 --> 10:29.456
Shang notes of farewell.

10:30.456 --> 10:31.736
Yu signifies sorrow.

10:32.136 --> 10:33.815
Yunsong's song

10:34.055 --> 10:35.935
suits this farewell feast quite well.

10:36.136 --> 10:36.935
Indeed.

10:38.055 --> 10:40.976
He sings of parting
but also sings of himself.

10:41.775 --> 10:42.976
Full of despair,

10:44.655 --> 10:46.055
with so many ambitions,

10:47.935 --> 10:49.256
yet ultimately unfulfilled.

11:07.136 --> 11:08.856
Yunsong excels
in both poetry and painting.

11:09.616 --> 11:12.415
How could such a master
face such disappointments?

11:12.415 --> 11:13.336
Of course.

11:14.096 --> 11:17.736
Back when he first became
the Chief Secretary of Chuzhou,

11:18.136 --> 11:19.815
problems arose at Lishan Academy.

11:20.655 --> 11:22.456
He was implicated
and dismissed from office.

11:24.376 --> 11:26.456
Yunsong was a student at Lishan Academy?

11:27.415 --> 11:28.856
But he only stayed for half a month.

11:29.815 --> 11:30.616
He

11:31.616 --> 11:32.736
loves rich meats

11:33.256 --> 11:34.256
and is fond of wine,

11:34.935 --> 11:37.616
yet the academy food was bland.

11:37.815 --> 11:39.456
And he wasn't allowed to drink much.

11:39.616 --> 11:42.456
He found Lishan Mountain stifling.

11:42.775 --> 11:44.016
So he ran away with luggage.

11:46.815 --> 11:50.136
His stay was so short.
Why would he be implicated?

11:50.575 --> 11:54.935
While at Lishan Mountain, he wrote
several verses praising its scenery.

11:55.976 --> 11:57.736
Everyone knew he came
from Lishan Mountain.

11:58.016 --> 12:01.175
He was bound to be dragged in
when Lishan Academy got into trouble.

12:33.552 --> 12:38.022
♪The moonlight had scattered some dust♪

12:40.880 --> 12:45.311
♪And the cracks in memory were covered♪

12:47.696 --> 12:51.700
♪When did something chip away inside♪

12:52.432 --> 12:58.966
♪It's flickering,
as if expectations were lost♪

13:04.136 --> 13:06.976
Lady Ye, can you sing?

13:07.376 --> 13:08.216
I do,

13:09.055 --> 13:12.216
but I fear you will all cover your ears
and run as soon as I open my mouth.

13:14.736 --> 13:17.456
What about playing the guqin?

13:18.415 --> 13:19.655
I do play drums a bit.

13:20.136 --> 13:20.736
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

13:20.976 --> 13:21.476
Show us!

13:21.476 --> 13:21.976
Bravo!

13:21.976 --> 13:23.216
Lady Ye, liven things up!

13:23.216 --> 13:24.415
- Show us!
- Yes!

13:24.415 --> 13:25.175
Bravo!

13:27.152 --> 13:30.544
♪You don't have to chase♪

13:30.544 --> 13:33.968
♪After clouds that winds pursue♪

13:33.968 --> 13:37.332
♪You can silently watch each sunrise♪

13:37.332 --> 13:40.893
♪Finding happiness by your side♪

13:40.893 --> 13:44.375
♪You don't need to chart a map♪

13:44.375 --> 13:47.739
♪Of every bend where love winds on♪

13:47.739 --> 13:51.190
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

13:51.190 --> 13:53.296
♪To warm♪

13:53.296 --> 13:56.496
♪Your heart♪

13:58.856 --> 13:59.935
Thank you.

14:00.456 --> 14:02.415
You helped me depict the Divine Maiden.

14:02.575 --> 14:03.856
I presented you with a painting.

14:04.175 --> 14:05.136
You help me,

14:05.216 --> 14:06.175
and I repay you.

14:06.216 --> 14:07.136
With debts reconciled.

14:07.136 --> 14:08.736
(Zhengyi Temple)

14:08.736 --> 14:12.055
Abbott, thank you for hosting me
these past days. I must take my leave.

14:12.736 --> 14:13.856
Travel well.

14:14.016 --> 14:15.655
Li, you go ahead.

14:16.496 --> 14:18.895
I plan to linger longer
in this serene place.

14:20.784 --> 14:23.984
♪They lifted you
with broadest shoulders♪

14:24.880 --> 14:27.096
♪To soar in skies above♪

14:27.096 --> 14:28.976
Please return, everyone.

14:29.616 --> 14:30.256
Here.

14:36.376 --> 14:37.136
Let's go.

14:46.856 --> 14:47.655
Hold on tight.

15:17.616 --> 15:19.415
You seemed so happy while drinking.

15:20.016 --> 15:22.016
Why are you now drooping
like a wilted flower?

15:23.175 --> 15:25.136
Drunk, you were either
singing or dancing

15:26.136 --> 15:28.216
and insisted on making Yunsong
teach you pipa.

15:28.616 --> 15:30.055
You even broke several strings.

15:31.440 --> 15:32.456
Wei Zhuang stopped you.

15:32.456 --> 15:35.575
But you then tried to drag others
into drinking games and bets.

15:36.055 --> 15:37.415
Win, and you raced around.

15:37.616 --> 15:41.016
Lose, and you feigned death,
pretending ignorance.

15:41.415 --> 15:43.016
If you hadn't sobered up in the end,

15:43.055 --> 15:44.336
you wouldn't have followed me.

15:49.216 --> 15:50.575
Stop talking.

15:51.016 --> 15:52.736
You've repeated this endlessly.

15:52.736 --> 15:54.616
I will etch this into your memory.

15:54.976 --> 15:56.456
This time, I was here.

15:57.055 --> 15:58.856
What if I'm not there next time?

15:59.616 --> 16:01.616
I haven't been this drunk in ages.

16:02.016 --> 16:04.616
At the mansion,
I never dared drink deeply.

16:04.616 --> 16:05.856
But you drank plenty.

16:06.935 --> 16:09.456
Don't think I don't know
what's in that little flask of yours.

16:10.575 --> 16:12.216
You sneak a drink from it now and then.

16:12.256 --> 16:15.256
You even lie to others, calling it
your health-boosting Qibao Tea.

16:19.815 --> 16:22.935
Your Highness,
can't you just be more formidable

16:23.136 --> 16:24.336
and shut his sharp tongue?

16:27.175 --> 16:28.175
You have a way?

16:28.376 --> 16:30.136
Yes, do you want to hear it?

16:31.055 --> 16:32.016
Do tell.

16:33.175 --> 16:34.736
The next time he scolds you,

16:35.736 --> 16:36.856
kiss him.

16:37.575 --> 16:38.856
Kiss him until he's breathless

16:39.055 --> 16:40.456
and can't open his mouth!

16:50.616 --> 16:51.456
It's so hot.

17:13.295 --> 17:15.095
Jin! Jin!

17:33.375 --> 17:34.176
What's wrong?

17:34.456 --> 17:35.535
Bandits blocking the road.

17:35.896 --> 17:36.736
No need to panic.

17:37.375 --> 17:38.615
I'll go speak with them first.

17:43.055 --> 17:46.176
Esteemed Gentlemen,
you're only after wealth, right?

17:46.335 --> 17:48.095
Surely there's no need for violence.

17:49.016 --> 17:52.016
I am Feng Zhiyao
from the Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

17:52.696 --> 17:55.135
I have friends
in all the martial world sects.

17:56.295 --> 17:59.176
But I understand your rule:
you can't leave empty-handed.

17:59.496 --> 18:02.216
Take this bag of gold
to buy your brothers some good wine.

18:03.135 --> 18:04.295
Don't be polite with me, now.

18:07.696 --> 18:10.016
Taking payment and clearing trouble?

18:10.295 --> 18:11.696
You know the principles, brother.

18:13.335 --> 18:14.496
Martial world's rules.

18:16.416 --> 18:19.095
It's just a misunderstanding.

18:20.896 --> 18:21.696
Take them!

18:30.216 --> 18:32.095
Lady Ye, get Mo Lao'er
out of here first!

18:32.416 --> 18:33.855
Your Highness, hold on tight.

18:46.335 --> 18:46.835
After them!

19:33.295 --> 19:34.095
Your Highness!

19:36.615 --> 19:37.416
Ye Li!

19:38.016 --> 19:39.096
Your Highness.

19:39.096 --> 19:40.535
- Are you alright?
- Are you okay?

19:44.815 --> 19:45.656
Quick, hide!

19:57.496 --> 19:58.295
Hurry!

20:00.216 --> 20:01.016
Stay quiet!

20:01.575 --> 20:02.216
Search!

20:03.575 --> 20:05.575
Where are they? Search!

20:08.095 --> 20:09.295
Stay hidden and don't move.

20:09.295 --> 20:10.535
Wait for Feng Zhiyao to come.

20:10.535 --> 20:11.456
What are you doing?

20:11.456 --> 20:12.615
I'm going to draw them away.

20:12.855 --> 20:14.496
If we both hide here, we'll both die.

20:14.496 --> 20:15.216
No!

20:15.216 --> 20:15.976
Ye Li!

20:16.615 --> 20:17.216
Ye Li!

20:18.416 --> 20:19.016
She's there!

20:20.216 --> 20:20.815
Go!

20:21.256 --> 20:21.855
Go!

20:22.216 --> 20:22.815
There she is!

20:25.535 --> 20:26.135
Hurry!

20:28.535 --> 20:29.295
Get her!

20:29.295 --> 20:29.896
Stop!

21:03.575 --> 21:04.176
Stop!

21:15.095 --> 21:15.696
Go!

21:16.696 --> 21:17.335
Get him!

21:42.416 --> 21:43.416
Who are you?

21:44.736 --> 21:45.575
Your name?

21:47.095 --> 21:48.135
Who sent you?

21:48.736 --> 21:49.855
I asked your name.

21:51.896 --> 21:53.375
Are you Princess Ding, Ye Li?

21:55.295 --> 21:57.936
You're not with the earlier group?

21:58.095 --> 21:59.055
Not of your concern.

21:59.815 --> 22:02.295
Just tell me. Are you...

22:11.496 --> 22:12.295
Your Highness!

22:18.135 --> 22:18.936
Stop!

22:21.896 --> 22:22.736
Stop running!

22:37.736 --> 22:40.256
Oh no, oh no!

22:49.055 --> 22:51.775
Sir, why doesn't this person
speak at all?

22:53.055 --> 22:54.496
Sir, stop for a bit.

22:58.176 --> 22:59.855
He's burning up. He's very ill.

23:00.135 --> 23:02.335
Wake up. How do you feel?

23:05.055 --> 23:05.936
Master, you're awake?

23:07.295 --> 23:08.256
How did I get here?

23:08.855 --> 23:09.736
Your fever was severe.

23:10.016 --> 23:11.736
If a lady hadn't
brought you here in time,

23:11.855 --> 23:12.880
you'd be in grave danger.

23:14.335 --> 23:15.055
How much do I owe?

23:16.496 --> 23:17.535
No need, master.

23:17.815 --> 23:20.055
The lady who brought you here
has already paid your fee.

23:58.295 --> 23:59.095
Mo Lao'er?

23:59.456 --> 24:00.256
Your Highness?

24:00.775 --> 24:01.615
Feng Zhiyao!

24:03.896 --> 24:04.736
Jin!

24:05.416 --> 24:06.216
This way!

24:09.416 --> 24:10.216
Mo Lao'er!

24:10.575 --> 24:11.855
Your Highness, are you alright?

24:11.855 --> 24:12.615
Go save Ye Li!

24:12.688 --> 24:13.335
Your Highness?

24:13.335 --> 24:14.176
She went that way.

24:14.176 --> 24:14.976
You've already...

24:14.976 --> 24:15.615
Hurry!

24:17.575 --> 24:18.375
Take care of him.

24:18.375 --> 24:19.256
Stay safe.

24:22.375 --> 24:23.295
Are you injured?

24:46.976 --> 24:47.775
Your Highness?

25:10.656 --> 25:12.416
That group from earlier was strange.

25:12.936 --> 25:15.216
They neither took our money
nor our lives.

25:15.335 --> 25:17.896
They had barely fought with Jin
before turning and fleeing.

25:18.288 --> 25:19.952
What kind of 'trouble clearing' is that?

25:20.416 --> 25:21.216
Your Highness.

25:21.936 --> 25:22.535
Your Highness.

25:22.535 --> 25:23.335
Where is my wife?

25:24.295 --> 25:25.095
I haven't found her.

25:26.095 --> 25:27.936
I've searched every place in the woods.

25:27.936 --> 25:29.656
I only found
a trail of women's footprints.

25:29.656 --> 25:30.976
I followed them to the cliff edge

25:32.135 --> 25:33.416
and only found this.

25:35.335 --> 25:36.936
Isn't it from Her Highness's attire?

25:43.055 --> 25:44.535
This drawing depicts Her Highness.

25:45.295 --> 25:46.976
Could it be they were targeting her?

25:47.375 --> 25:48.176
Take me there.

25:48.656 --> 25:49.416
You...

25:49.855 --> 25:51.375
Your legs aren't steady.

25:51.456 --> 25:53.535
By the time we carried you there,
it would be dark,

25:53.535 --> 25:54.815
making it impossible to search.

25:55.416 --> 25:57.535
We should escort you
back to the mansion first.

25:57.736 --> 26:01.016
Jin, return immediately
to report any news.

26:05.416 --> 26:08.176
Not the mansion.
To Zhengyi Temple, alright?

26:08.496 --> 26:09.896
Zhengyi Temple is closer.

26:10.335 --> 26:12.615
Better than sitting here waiting idly.

26:12.615 --> 26:14.936
Jin, continue searching
at the cliff edge.

26:14.936 --> 26:15.615
Understood.

26:21.136 --> 26:21.855
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

26:21.855 --> 26:23.216
Go to Jingzhao Prefecture for me.

26:23.216 --> 26:24.496
Show my token and rally men.

26:24.496 --> 26:26.936
Be swift. We must find her.

26:29.256 --> 26:30.055
I'm counting on you.

26:35.295 --> 26:36.095
Your Highness!

26:37.375 --> 26:38.176
Your Highness!

26:54.176 --> 26:54.976
Your Highness?

26:57.216 --> 26:58.016
Your Highness?

27:25.176 --> 27:26.335
Why is she still burning?

27:32.656 --> 27:33.456
Li.

27:34.496 --> 27:35.615
I'm alright.

27:37.656 --> 27:38.456
What?

27:42.736 --> 27:43.815
Mo Xiuyao,

27:45.375 --> 27:46.375
don't worry.

28:06.224 --> 28:09.328
(Songyue Mountain Villa)

28:28.256 --> 28:29.055
Lady?

28:30.696 --> 28:33.295
You're awake? She's awake!

28:57.456 --> 28:58.608
(Songyue Mountain Villa)

29:04.775 --> 29:07.176
Was my eye condition
caused by a venomous snake?

29:07.775 --> 29:10.936
You fell from a cliff and were bitten
by a white-striped snake.

29:11.055 --> 29:12.855
Its venom is extremely potent.

29:13.055 --> 29:16.095
The toxins entered through your arm,
affected your meridians,

29:16.095 --> 29:19.016
and reached your brain,
thus impairing your sight.

29:19.416 --> 29:20.656
Will I go blind?

29:21.375 --> 29:22.775
Please rest assured.

29:23.256 --> 29:25.176
The harm is temporary.

29:25.256 --> 29:27.696
Once the meridians recover
and all toxins dissipate,

29:27.855 --> 29:28.976
your sight will return.

29:29.135 --> 29:30.095
How long will it take?

29:31.216 --> 29:32.815
Slowly, seven or eight days.

29:32.815 --> 29:34.416
Swiftly, two to three days.

29:36.696 --> 29:37.736
Thank you, physician.

29:42.535 --> 29:44.696
Take this medicine once daily.

29:46.375 --> 29:47.375
Thank you, physician.

29:47.456 --> 29:48.256
This way, please.

29:59.535 --> 30:01.016
Lady, I'll pour you some water.

30:08.615 --> 30:10.016
Here, water.

30:13.615 --> 30:16.016
Lady, the physician mentioned earlier

30:16.055 --> 30:18.055
that mixing medicines
isn't suited for you now.

30:18.335 --> 30:20.896
He advised using loquat
for severe coughing.

30:20.896 --> 30:22.295
Shall Youlan fetch you some?

30:23.656 --> 30:24.496
That's not necessary.

30:26.055 --> 30:27.016
You are called Youlan?

30:27.855 --> 30:28.656
Yes.

30:29.055 --> 30:30.775
Thank you for tending
to me, Lady Youlan.

30:31.456 --> 30:32.656
You're too gracious.

30:32.656 --> 30:35.095
I serve you
under the villa lord's order.

30:36.055 --> 30:39.736
The villa lord? Did he rescue me?

30:39.976 --> 30:42.936
Indeed. This place
is called Songyue Mountain Villa.

30:43.976 --> 30:45.416
Who is your villa lord?

30:46.055 --> 30:49.135
The villa lord is the villa lord.

30:49.456 --> 30:51.295
We may not use his name directly.

30:53.055 --> 30:55.176
Can you take me to him?

30:55.416 --> 30:56.775
I wish to thank him in person.

30:57.696 --> 30:58.496
Well...

31:02.496 --> 31:03.656
I cannot decide.

31:03.936 --> 31:05.696
But I can inform the steward for you.

31:08.256 --> 31:10.855
Is Songyue Mountain Villa
far from the capital?

31:12.855 --> 31:14.176
I haven't visited the capital,

31:14.375 --> 31:16.295
but according
to the steward, it's not far.

31:16.295 --> 31:17.535
Just half a day's journey.

31:18.815 --> 31:21.176
Alright, you may go ahead.

31:22.295 --> 31:23.095
Yes.

31:23.375 --> 31:24.176
Please.

31:25.295 --> 31:27.216
Could you find me a walking stick?

31:27.496 --> 31:29.216
It would help me move around the room.

31:30.496 --> 31:31.295
Yes.

31:31.575 --> 31:34.936
Later I'll place a jug of water
by the bedside table,

31:35.256 --> 31:36.696
easily within your grasp.

31:37.656 --> 31:38.496
I take my leave.

32:13.456 --> 32:15.615
This medicine is made by me.

32:15.775 --> 32:18.496
I added almonds.
Good for your stomach and warms you.

32:20.055 --> 32:22.295
Could you come back
and join us for dinner?

32:32.368 --> 32:32.976
Your Highness.

32:32.976 --> 32:33.656
Well?

32:33.976 --> 32:35.416
We searched the bottom of the cliff.

32:36.375 --> 32:37.815
We only found this.

32:38.535 --> 32:40.736
Is it Her Highness's shoe?

32:42.815 --> 32:45.656
But we found no trace of Her Highness.

32:50.656 --> 32:52.016
There's no need to worry.

32:52.135 --> 32:54.016
Rotting leaves pile thick at the bottom.

32:54.135 --> 32:56.535
Even if she slipped and fell,
with the leaves as a cushion,

32:57.815 --> 32:59.496
it's very likely she survived.

33:01.055 --> 33:01.855
However,

33:03.095 --> 33:04.295
venomous snakes dwell there.

33:04.295 --> 33:06.016
We don't know
if Her Highness was bitten.

33:08.815 --> 33:09.615
Snakes?

33:11.375 --> 33:14.256
One more odd thing
I couldn't figure out on the way back.

33:15.976 --> 33:17.615
I found this at the bottom.

33:17.976 --> 33:21.575
I suspect there might be
a sword master at the bottom

33:21.896 --> 33:24.575
who used a branch
as a sword to kill the snakes

33:24.775 --> 33:25.855
and rescued Her Highness.

33:29.815 --> 33:31.456
Word has come from Master Feng.

33:31.456 --> 33:33.335
They've located those bandits.

33:40.176 --> 33:43.327
(Songyue Mountain Villa)

34:02.375 --> 34:04.496
Any... Anyone here?

34:08.055 --> 34:09.255
What time is it?

34:34.456 --> 34:35.336
Is anyone here?

34:53.016 --> 34:54.416
How come there's no one?

35:29.416 --> 35:30.215
Thank you.

35:33.856 --> 35:35.336
Are you part of the villa?

35:36.135 --> 35:37.655
Do you know where the villa lord is?

35:41.376 --> 35:42.296
My name is Ye.

35:43.095 --> 35:44.655
I fell from a cliff a few days ago

35:45.296 --> 35:46.896
and was rescued by the villa lord here.

35:47.816 --> 35:49.215
I wish to thank him in person.

35:50.575 --> 35:53.376
A maid said she would pass on
my message during the day.

35:54.095 --> 35:55.856
But then I never saw her again.

35:56.456 --> 35:57.976
And my room's been empty.

35:58.856 --> 36:00.376
So I came out to look.

36:01.976 --> 36:03.856
But my eyes can't see now.

36:04.976 --> 36:06.496
Can you lead the way?

36:13.175 --> 36:16.255
Are you unable to speak?

36:23.615 --> 36:24.976
Thank you anyway.

37:15.215 --> 37:17.016
Are you the physician's disciple

37:18.016 --> 37:19.695
or a servant of this villa?

37:23.215 --> 37:24.776
If you truly can't speak,

37:24.816 --> 37:26.695
could you please
find someone else to help me?

38:08.615 --> 38:09.416
Wait.

38:11.535 --> 38:13.016
Could you deliver a message for me?

38:13.575 --> 38:15.496
I haven't returned home
for several days.

38:15.816 --> 38:17.296
My family must be worried.

38:18.456 --> 38:20.776
Please deliver a message to my husband.

38:21.336 --> 38:23.816
Tell him where I am
so he can come for me.

38:24.655 --> 38:27.095
My husband is Prince Ding, Mo Xiuyao.

38:27.535 --> 38:29.655
Find him, and he will surely repay you.

38:44.896 --> 38:45.695
I'll talk.

38:47.735 --> 38:48.695
I was just...

38:50.735 --> 38:52.255
I was just there to help her.

38:52.376 --> 38:53.575
Don't think I don't know.

38:53.936 --> 38:55.575
You're the one who tossed her off.

38:55.735 --> 38:57.416
Talk now, and suffer less.

38:57.655 --> 39:00.535
Our villa lord's patience
isn't as good as mine.

39:01.456 --> 39:02.255
Going to talk?

39:04.976 --> 39:06.695
Talk! Talk!

39:11.175 --> 39:12.016
Talk!

39:24.655 --> 39:25.856
Who are you?

39:26.456 --> 39:27.615
Who sent you?

39:30.095 --> 39:31.416
That woman...

39:34.416 --> 39:36.215
I'm asking you!

39:37.376 --> 39:40.336
Is... Is she still alive?

39:47.255 --> 39:48.055
Not talking?

39:58.215 --> 39:59.016
Your Highness.

40:13.856 --> 40:15.735
Your Highness, you summoned me?

40:17.055 --> 40:18.135
He's with Tianyi Pavilion.

40:28.336 --> 40:29.215
Han Mingxi?

40:30.655 --> 40:32.095
He's Han Mingyue's younger brother.

40:32.095 --> 40:34.376
I've seen him once before. No mistake.

40:34.816 --> 40:36.856
After the fire
at the Eastern Palace years ago,

40:36.856 --> 40:40.255
the Hans, loyal to the Crown Prince,
were purged by Marquis Muyang.

40:40.735 --> 40:43.936
Only the two brothers
survived the journey of exile.

40:46.416 --> 40:48.416
I hear his martial skills are mediocre

40:48.655 --> 40:51.615
and his temperament
is nothing like his older brother's.

40:52.135 --> 40:55.776
Word is he quarreled
with Han Mingyue recently and left home.

40:55.936 --> 40:58.615
Who knew he'd come to the capital.

41:04.776 --> 41:06.416
So why would he want to kill Li?

41:07.856 --> 41:08.695
Well...

41:14.316 --> 41:15.055
- Come on!
- Good!

41:15.055 --> 41:15.816
Come on!

41:15.816 --> 41:17.095
All in on big!

41:17.095 --> 41:18.535
- On big!
- All in on small!

41:19.816 --> 41:20.535
More wine?

41:20.776 --> 41:21.296
Have another!

41:21.936 --> 41:22.535
Cheers!

41:22.535 --> 41:23.095
Bottoms up!

41:23.095 --> 41:23.595
Come on!

41:23.776 --> 41:24.296
Drink!

41:27.175 --> 41:27.695
Come on!

41:30.175 --> 41:30.976
Go take a look.

41:32.376 --> 41:32.896
Let's go.

41:33.976 --> 41:35.016
Alright, keep going.

41:39.655 --> 41:41.135
Who goes there at this hour?

41:42.016 --> 41:43.615
A trader from over the mountains.

41:44.175 --> 41:45.936
Too early. No business now.

41:46.575 --> 41:47.376
No?

41:47.376 --> 41:48.336
It's a big deal.

42:09.175 --> 42:09.976
Let's go!

42:20.856 --> 42:21.655
Where is she?

42:23.416 --> 42:24.215
'She'?

42:27.215 --> 42:27.896
Who is 'she'?

42:31.028 --> 42:33.529
(Preview)

42:33.856 --> 42:34.960
(Where do you think you are?)

42:35.655 --> 42:36.304
(Lishan Mountain?)

42:37.135 --> 42:37.896
(A Daoist temple?)

42:38.655 --> 42:39.496
(Free to come and go?)

42:40.135 --> 42:43.296
You're gone for a full day today,
sending back no word.

42:44.135 --> 42:45.776
Do you think you are some roaming hero?

42:46.175 --> 42:49.535
You're blaming
those people's deaths on me?

42:50.496 --> 42:51.496
You want to kill me?

42:52.175 --> 42:54.896
Kill me! Come on, kill me!

42:57.655 --> 42:58.296
You're insane!

42:59.336 --> 43:00.175
The next cut

43:01.456 --> 43:02.535
will go here.

43:03.936 --> 43:05.776
It's that foolish woman,
that foolish woman!

43:15.696 --> 43:22.288
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.872 --> 43:32.016
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.224 --> 43:37.456
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.680 --> 43:43.696
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.016 --> 43:47.440
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.504 --> 43:54.064
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.120 --> 43:59.056
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.056 --> 44:04.752
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.264 --> 44:13.872
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.768 --> 44:20.272
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.272 --> 44:25.776
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.840 --> 44:29.904
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.192 --> 44:35.416
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.016 --> 44:39.728
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.760 --> 44:45.424
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.192 --> 44:54.160
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.568 --> 45:00.816
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.072 --> 45:06.976
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.976 --> 45:11.096
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.312 --> 45:16.048
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.264 --> 45:21.536
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.776 --> 45:27.216
♪Unbound by form♪
